---
import herbert from "../assets/herbert.webp";
import FadeIn from "./fade-in";
import Heading from "./heading";
---

<section class="bg-white">
  <div
    class="from-brand-green to-brand-blue overflow-visible bg-linear-to-r px-0 py-12 pb-0 lg:px-10 lg:py-30"
  >
    <div
      class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col-reverse gap-12 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:gap-20"
    >
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
        <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto w-full lg:mx-0 lg:-mb-92">
          <img
            src={herbert.src}
            alt="Dr. Herbert Maradiaga"
            class="aspect-video w-full object-cover object-center lg:aspect-square"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Signature intentionally hidden for now. -->
      </div>

      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
        <Heading
          client:visible
          as="h2"
          size="0"
          className="text-center tracking-[0.28em] text-white uppercase lg:text-left"
        >
          Feel Better<br />
          Than Ever
        </Heading>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="px-6 pt-12 pb-12 lg:px-10 lg:pt-16 lg:pb-16">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col gap-10 lg:flex-row">
      <div class="hidden lg:block lg:w-1/2"></div>

      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
        <FadeIn
          client:visible
          as="div"
          className="max-w-xl text-base leading-8 text-neutral-600 lg:text-lg"
          delay={0.1}
        >
          <p>
            Desde 2010 somos expertos en metabolismo, equilibrio hormonal y
            bienestar integral. Hemos construido clínicas especializadas donde
            la experiencia médica y la tecnología avanzada trabajan para una
            sola meta:
            <span class="block font-medium text-neutral-700 uppercase">
              que te sientas mejor que nunca.
            </span>
          </p>

          <p class="mt-7">
            Por eso nuestro lema es Feel Better Than Ever. No es solo un slogan.
            Es una promesa.
          </p>
        </FadeIn>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
